TRIGGER

AIM
To create a trigger that automatically assign/display grade based on student marks.


Algorithm

1. Start
2. Create a trigger with BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE
3. Check marks using IF condition
4. Assign grades accordingly
5. End trigger
6. Insert or update student record
7. Stop


Query

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER_GRADE_Hi
BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE
ON STUDENT
FOR EACH ROW

BEGIN

IF :NEW.MARKS >= 90 THEN
:NEW.GRADE := 'A';

ELSIF :NEW.MARKS >= 75 THEN
:NEW.GRADE := 'B';

ELSIF :NEW.MARKS >= 50 THEN
:NEW.GRADE := 'C';

ELSE
:NEW.GRADE := 'F';

END IF;

END;
/
